face_mask.Description: Whether a mask was worn during the session. REDCap: fmri_face_mask.

t1_tech_rating.Description: Rating of the T1 given by the Technologist. REDCap: fmricufft1techrating,fmricufft1techrating2.

cuff1_pressure_from_qst.Description: Cuff pressure to achieve 4/10 pain during Quantitative Sensory Testing (QST). REDCap: fmri_dt_1 (mmHg).

cuff1_recalibrated_pressure.Description: Cuff pressure to acheive 4/10 pain rating, if recalibrated. REDCap: fmricuffcalfpressurerecal (mmHg).

cuff1_applied_pressure.Description: Pressure that was expected to be applied during CUFF1 (mmHg). For actual pressure, see *events.tsv.

surgical_site_pain_rest.Description: Surgical site pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffrestpainss.

body_pain_rest.Description: Body pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffrestpainovrall.

surgical_site_pain_after_first_scan.LongName: Surgical Site Pain After First Scan
surgical_site_pain_after_first_scan.Description: Surgical site pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffcurrpainaftfirstscanss.

body_pain_after_first_scan.Description: Body pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffcurrpainaftfirstscanovrall.

cuff_pain_cuff1_beginning.Description: Cuff pain during first third of CUFF1 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainbegin.

cuff_pain_cuff1_middle.Description: Cuff pain during second third of CUFF1 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainmid.

cuff_pain_cuff1_end.Description: Cuff pain during final third of CUFF1 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainend.

cuff_pain_cuff2_beginning.Description: Cuff pain during first third of CUFF2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpaincpbegin.

cuff_pain_cuff2_middle.Description: Cuff pain during second third of CUFF2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpaincpmid.

cuff_pain_cuff2_end.Description: Cuff pain during final third of CUFF2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpaincpend.

cuff_pain_rest_beginning.Description: Cuff pain during first third of REST2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainrestscanbegin.

cuff_pain_rest_middle.Description: Cuff pain during second third of REST2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainrestscanmid.

cuff_pain_rest_end.Description: Cuff pain during final third of REST2 (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainrestscanend.

surgical_site_pain_after_last_scan.LongName: Surgical Site Pain After Last Scan
surgical_site_pain_after_last_scan.Description: Surgical site pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainaftlastscanss.

body_pain_after_last_scan.Description: Body pain (range: 0 - 10, allow 0.5 increments). REDCap: fmricuffpainaftlastscanany.

cuff_contraindicated.Description: Whether cuff pressure was contraindicated. REDCap: fmricuffcontrayn,cuffpfmricontraindyn.

deviceserialnumber.Description: Serial number of scanner used to collect scans

cull_leg.Description: Leg on which cuff pressure was applied. In TKA patients, this is the leg that is not receiving surgery.
